---
import PageHero from "@/components/PageHero.astro";
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Project Request Received | AlfaRank">
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Request received"
    title="Your project request has been submitted."
    text="AlfaRank will review the project type, business problem, current system, and desired result before the next step."
    primaryHref="/"
    primaryLabel="Back to Home"
    secondaryHref="/capabilities/"
    secondaryLabel="Explore Capabilities"
  />

  <section class="section split-panel">
    <div class="glass-panel">
      <h2>What happens next</h2>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>The request is reviewed against the relevant system type.</li>
        <li>The current website, workflow, or infrastructure is checked if provided.</li>
        <li>The next step is defined around scope, feasibility, timeline, and implementation path.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="glass-panel">
      <h2>Useful context</h2>
      <p>If more details are needed, the follow-up will focus on business output, existing systems, required integrations, and what should be launched first.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
